      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0045"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Österreich</rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb428">Welsberg im Pustertal</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb423">Tirol</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><seg><seg rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0046"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142880">Swinemünde</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb145807">Strand</rs></hi></hi></seg></seg></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0046"/><date when="1907-08-07">7. 8. 07</date>. Ich war <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb142880">hier</rs>, um über die <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03255-1"/>Kri<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en-<hi rend="latintype">Entrevue</hi><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03255-1">Gemeint war das Treffen zwischen <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2566">Kaiser Wilhelm II.</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2996">Zar Nikolaus II.</rs> am <date when="1907-08-04">4. 8. 1907</date> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb142880">Swinemünde</rs>.
               </note> zu berichten. Herzliche Grüße Dir, <salute>lieber Freund,</salute> u. Deiner
                  <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs>. Näch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Woche gehe
               ich auf Urlaub, aber ich weiß noch immer nicht, wohin. Dein <signed>Paul
                  Goldmann.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
